data.title: Learn German with Online Magazines
data.meta_description: Welcome to our online German magazine pages, featuring online magazines, journals and other electronic print formats from Germany!   More Magazines from around the world Online magazines and journals fill this need in a useful manner, for they present modern prose with a more challenging vocabulary than that found in n
